Amazing landscapes, flawless organization
Mar 2024 Solo
Very friendly staff, good advice to choose the tour. I visited Ninh Binh area, Hoa Lu, Trang An and Mua Cave. The landscapes were absolutely amazing ! The part in bicycle was also quite fun. We were free to move around on our own overall, and the guidance was just the right amount I feel.

On the tour, the guide (Chung) was very friendly. Chung's English was sometimes a bit hard to understand for a non English native like me, but overall he was doing fine. Could have been nice to have a bit more insight about a couple of places, but I do value freedom as well so it's good too. We had another guide, Alex, for one part of the tour (Hoa Lu), who was more fluent in English and gave us some insight.

The bus was very comfortable, the buffet was good, we had just the good amount of time for everything we did that day. We were picked up and brought back at our hotels and the timing was well respected.
